node.text: IN HONOR OF TODAY’S 20th ANNIVERSARY OF “LEGALLY BLONDE” (a religious holiday in my house) I’M REVISITING THIS 2015 @vanityfair INTERVIEW WITH @reesewitherspoon WHEN I PITCHED A SEQUEL WITH ELLE WOODS AS A SUPREME COURT JUSTICE! 👩🏼‍💼⚖️💘

Last week’s haute couture shows were about breaking boundaries (@kerbito for @pyermoss), revisiting history (@demnagvasalia for @balenciaga), bringing back bridal glamour (@virginieviard for @chanelofficial), and so much more. I was on diaper duty this season (last slide, couldn’t help myself!), so I watched them all from home—and you can too on YouTube.com/Fashion
